message: "If you use this software, please cite using this metadata."
title: "agi-forecast — Lutar-Forecast Gauge: receipt-attested AGI capability gauges"
abstract: >-
  Module tracking 12 typed AGI capability gauge variables from authoritative upstream sources (METR,
  Epoch AI, ARC Prize, Apollo Research, AISI, Anthropic RSP, OpenAI Preparedness, DeepMind FSF,
  Stanford HAI AI Index). Each gauge value is stored with cryptographic provenance and emits a daily
  forecast receipt verifiable against the ouroboros replay root. Part of the SZL Holdings governed
  AI decision infrastructure.
